# SmartPepper Web Dashboard - Environment Configuration

# IPFS Configuration
# Choose ONE of the following options:

# ===== OPTION 1: Mock Mode (Development - No Setup Required) =====
# Uses mock CIDs for testing. No actual IPFS upload.
# Leave all IPFS variables commented out to use this mode automatically.

# ===== OPTION 2: Local IPFS Node (Recommended for Development) =====
# 1. Download IPFS Desktop: https://docs.ipfs.tech/install/ipfs-desktop/
# 2. Install and start IPFS Desktop
# 3. Uncomment the line below:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_IPFS_PROVIDER=local

# ===== OPTION 3: Infura (Recommended for Production) =====
# 1. Sign up at https://infura.io/
# 2. Create an IPFS project
# 3. Copy your Project ID and Project Secret
# 4. Uncomment and fill in the values below:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_IPFS_PROVIDER=infura
# NEXT_PUBLIC_INFURA_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id_here
# NEXT_PUBLIC_INFURA_PROJECT_SECRET=your_project_secret_here

# ===== OPTION 4: Pinata (Alternative Cloud IPFS) =====
# NEXT_PUBLIC_IPFS_PROVIDER=pinata
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PINATA_JWT=your_pinata_jwt_here

# Blockchain Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0x5FbDB2315678afecb367f032d93F642f64180aa3
